# Frontend Rules — Landing Page

## Component Patterns
- Section components in components/home/
- Cart components in components/cart/
- Product components in components/producto/
- Catalog in components/home/CatalogoClient.tsx (main catalog logic)

## Animations (Framer Motion)
- Always use variants for stagger animations
- Fade + slide up for section entries
- Scale for button interactions
- Never remove existing animations — enhance them

## Tailwind Conventions
- Premium dark theme: bg-gray-900, bg-black, bg-zinc-900
- Accent gold: text-[#c89b6e], border-[#c89b6e]
- Cards: rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all
- Images: object-cover w-full h-full (always)

## Cart & Wishlist
- CartContext: addToCart(product, qty, size, color)
- WishlistContext: addToWishlist(productId), isInWishlist(productId)
- Both persist in localStorage (key: lukess-cart, lukess-wishlist)
- Show toast confirmation on add

## Checkout Flow (3 steps)
1. Customer data form (name, phone, email optional)
2. QR payment (Yolo Pago) — creates order in Supabase
3. Confirmation with confetti + WhatsApp button
